Sweet Tooth (001 - 040) (2009 - 2013) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerPhDemons)


Sweet Tooth is a story about a special Hybrid boy named Gus. Unlike most other Hybrids, Gus was not born conventionally, but in a lab. Gus also predates the arrival of the Hybrid children and is believed to be the key to unlock the mysteries in this post-apocalyptic tale. Gus is joined with his "protector" Tommy Jepperd, Doctor Singh and a band of Hybrid children.
